MLX and mlx-lm
    https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx
    https://github.com/ml-explore/mlx-lm
    License: MIT, Copyright (c) Apple Inc.

PonyExl3 builds on MLX (arrays, Metal kernels) and loads models into mlx-lm
model skeletons (Qwen3.5 / Qwen3.6 architectures). These are used as
dependencies; no MLX or mlx-lm source is vendored into this repository.
